  "body": "This issue https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/8348 found that something made closing the app hang.\r\n\r\nIt turns out, it was the  `FetchingHistoryTimer`, because it lasts 20 minutes and threads in Nim suck. You can find more information on the problem and the lines causing issue here: https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/8485\r\n\r\nThat code should be moved to status-go. In theory, it should be simple, it's a timer. The code that the timer calls can also be moved to status-go, since it just calls `checkRecentHistory` (with some conditions). The rest is handled by signals already.\r\n",
